prmwqmw qoN iv`Q pwaux vwlI (prmwqmw dI) mwieAw (hI hY ijs ny) jgq dy jIvW dy mnW ivc Awpxw itkwxw bxwieAw hoieAw hY[
(ies mwieAw qoN pYdw hoey) kwm kRoD AhMkwr (Awidk ivkwr jIvW dy Awqmk jIvn dw) nws kr dyNdy hn ]1]
ikqy BI aus qoN ibnw koeI hor nhIN hY[ aus pRBU qoN v`Krw (v`KrI hoNd vwlw) mYN koeI BI d`s nhIN skdw[
swry jIvW ivc iek auhI prmwqmw v`s irhw hY, ijs auqy mwieAw dw pRBwv nhIN pY skdw ]1] rhwau]
prmwqmw qoN iv`Q pYdw krn vwlI (mwieAw dy kwrn hI mnu`K dI) BYVI m`q (mnu`K nUM) d`sdI rihMdI hY ik mwieAw dI hsqI pRBU qoN v`KrI hY[
(ies durmq dy Asr hyT) jIv jMmdw hY mrdw hY jMmdw hY mrdw hY, (ies qrHW) Awqmk mOqy mr ky prmwqmw qoN iv`Q qy ho jWdw hY ]2]
pr mYN qW DrqI AwkwS ivc, (ikqy BI prmwqmw qoN ibnw) koeI hor hsqI nhIN vyKdw[
iesqRI purK ivc, swrI hI isRStI ivc prmwqmw nUM hI vyKdw hW ]3]
mYN sUrj cMdRmw (iehnW isRStI dy) dIivAW dw cwnx q`kdw hW[
swirAW dy AMdr iek-rs mYnUM sdw-jvwn pRIqm pRBU hI id`s irhw hY ]4]
siqgurU ny imhr kr ky myrw ic`q pRBU-crnW ivc joV id`qw,
qy mYnUM ieh smJ dy id`qI ik hr QW iek prmwqmw hI v`s irhw hY ]5]
jyhVw mnu`K gurU dy snmuK huMdw hY, auh ieh jwx lYNdw hY ik iek inrMjn hI hr QW mOjUd hY,
Aqy auh gur-Sbd dI brkiq nwl (Awpxy AMdroN) prmwqmw nwloN vKyvW mukw ky prmwqmw (dI hoNd) nUM pCwx lYNdw hY ]6]
swrI isRStI ivc isr& prmwqmw dw hI hukm c`l irhw hY[
iek prmwqmw qoN hI swrI auqp`qI hoeI hY ]7]
(iek pRBU qoN hI swrI auqp`qI hox qy BI mwieAw dy pRBwv hyT jgq ivc) dovyN rsqy c`l pYNdy hn (-gurmuKqw Aqy durmq)[ (pr sB ivc) iek prmwqmw nUM hI (vrqdw) jwx[
gurU dy Sbd ivc juV ky (swry jgq ivc prmwqmw dw hI) hukm c`ldw pCwx ]8]
jo swry rUpW ivc swry vrnW iv`c qy swry (jIvW dy) mnW ivc ivAwpk hY,
hy nwnk! mYN aus ie`k prmwqmw dI hI is&q-swlwh krdw hW ]9]5]
