jdoN mnu`K Awqmk jIvn nUM au~cw krn vwly krm krdw hY, qdoN hI s`cw (jogI) hY[
pr ijs dw mn ivkwrW dy twkry qy kmzor hY, auh ivkwrW qoN ^lwsI hwsl krn dy Byq nUM kIh jwx skdw hY? ]1]
Ajyhw (bMdw) jogI (AKvwx dw h`kdwr ho skdw hY jo jIvn dI shI) jugiq smJdw hY[
(auh jIvn-jugiq ieh hY ik kwmwidk) pMjW (ivkwrW) nUM mwr ky sdw kwiem rihx vwly prmwqmw (dI Xwd) nUM Awpxy ihrdy ivc itkWdw hY ]1] rhwau]
ijs mnu`K dy AMdr prmwqmw Awpxw sdw-iQr nwm vsWdw hY,
auh mnu`K pRBU-imlwp dI jugiq dI kdr smJdw hY ]2]
qpS, TMF (Bwv, iksy vloN KrHvw slUk qy iksy vloN in`Gw slUk) Gr, jMgl (Bwv, Gr ivc rihMidAW inrmoh rveIAw) aus nUM iek-smwn id`sdy hn[
prmwqmw dI is&q-swlwh-rUp krxI aus dw swmwn (swDwrn) krm hn (Bwv, suqy hI auh is&q-swlwh ivc juiVAw rihMdw hY) ]3]
